#. module: cooperator
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cooperator.email_template_confirmation
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"    Hello <t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t>,\n"
"    <br><br>\n"
"    Thank you for filling out the form and request to join the community <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t><t t-if=\"object.is_company\"> on behalf of <t t-out=\"object.company_name\"></t></t>.\n"
"    <br>\n"
"    In the coming weeks we will contact you to indicate the next steps.\n"
"    <br><br>\n"
"    Here is a copy of the data we received:\n"
"    <br><br>\n"
"        - Request to join: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.is_company\">\n"
"        - Company Name: <t t-out=\"object.company_name\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Company VAT: <t t-out=\"object.vat\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Company Email: <t t-out=\"object.company_email\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Representative firstname: <t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Representative lastname: <t t-out=\"object.lastname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Representative function: <t t-out=\"object.contact_person_function\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Representative email: <t t-out=\"object.email\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Representative phone: <t t-out=\"object.phone or ''\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Representative gender: <t t-out=\"dict(object.fields_get(allfields=['gender'])['gender']['selection'])[object.gender]\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Representative birthdate: <t t-out=\"object.birthdate\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-else=\"\">\n"
"        - VAT: <t t-out=\"object.vat\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Firstname: <t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Lastname: <t t-out=\"object.lastname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Email: <t t-out=\"object.email\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Phone: <t t-out=\"object.phone or ''\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Gender: <t t-out=\"dict(object.fields_get(allfields=['gender'])['gender']['selection'])[object.gender]\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Birthdate: <t t-out=\"object.birthdate\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"        - Address: <t t-out=\"object.address\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Zip code: <t t-out=\"object.zip_code\"></t><br>\n"
"        - City: <t t-out=\"object.city\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Country: <t t-out=\"object.country_id.name\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Language: <t t-out=\"dict(object.fields_get(allfields=['lang'])['lang']['selection'])[object.lang]\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Initial share amount: <t t-out=\"object.subscription_amount\"></t><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.payment_mode_id.payment_method_id.code == 'sepa_direct_debit'\">\n"
"        - Bank account: <t t-out=\"object.iban\"></t><br>\n"
"        - I authorize bank receipts to be sent to this account: <t t-out=\"object.mandate_approved and 'YES' or 'NOT'\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <br>\n"
"    We keep in touch for any questions.<br>\n"
"    <a href=\"https://somcomunitats.coop/recursos/\">Resources and FAQs</a><br><br>\n"
"    Yours faithfully,<br><br>\n"
"    <u><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t></u><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street2\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street2\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.city or object.company_id.zip\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.zip or ''),(object.company_id.city or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.country_id\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.state_id and ('%s, ' % object.company_id.state_id.name) or ''),(object.company_id.country_id.name or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.phone\">\n"
"        Phone: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.website\">\n"
"        Web: <a t-if=\"object.company_id.website\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"></t></a><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <div>\n"
"        <img t-if=\"object.company_id.logo_url\" t-att-src=\"('/web/image/res.company/%s/logo' % object.company_id.id)\" style=\"width: 150px;\">\n"
"    </div>\n"
"    </p>\n"
"</div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"    Hola <t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t>,\n"
"    <br><br>\n"
"    Gràcies per omplir el formulari i sol·licitar l’adhesió a la comunitat <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t><t t-if=\"object.is_company\"> en representació de <t t-out=\"object.company_name\"></t></t>.\n"
"    <br>\n"
"    En les properes setmanes ens posarem en contacte amb tu per indicar-te les següents passes.\n"
"    <br><br>\n"
"    Aquí tens una còpia de les dades que hem rebut:\n"
"    <br><br>\n"
"        - Sol·licitud per la comunitat: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.is_company\">\n"
"        - Nom empresa: <t t-out=\"object.company_name\"></t><br>\n"
"        - NIF/CIF empresa: <t t-out=\"object.vat\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Correu empresa: <t t-out=\"object.company_email\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Nom representant: <t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Cognoms representant: <t t-out=\"object.lastname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Càrrec representant: <t t-out=\"object.contact_person_function\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Correu representant: <t t-out=\"object.email\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Telèfon representant: <t t-out=\"object.phone or ''\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Gènere representant: <t t-out=\"dict(object.fields_get(allfields=['gender'])['gender']['selection'])[object.gender]\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Data neixement: <t t-out=\"object.birthdate\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-else=\"\">\n"
"        - NIF/CIF: <t t-out=\"object.vat\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Nom: <t t-out=\"object.firstname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Cognoms: <t t-out=\"object.lastname\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Correu: <t t-out=\"object.email\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Telèfon: <t t-out=\"object.phone or ''\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Gènere: <t t-out=\"dict(object.fields_get(allfields=['gender'])['gender']['selection'])[object.gender]\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Data neixement: <t t-out=\"object.birthdate\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"        - Adreça: <t t-out=\"object.address\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Codi postal: <t t-out=\"object.zip_code\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Ciutat: <t t-out=\"object.city\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Pais: <t t-out=\"object.country_id.name\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Idioma: <t t-out=\"dict(object.fields_get(allfields=['lang'])['lang']['selection'])[object.lang]\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Import aportació inicial: <t t-out=\"object.subscription_amount\"></t><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.payment_mode_id.payment_method_id.code == 'sepa_direct_debit'\">\n"
"        - Compte bancari: <t t-out=\"object.iban\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Autoritzo giros bancaris a aquest compte: <t t-out=\"object.mandate_approved and 'YES' or 'NOT'\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <br>\n"
"    Seguim en contacte per qualsevol dubte.<br>\n"
"    <a href=\"https://somcomunitats.coop/recursos/\">Resources and FAQs</a><br><br>\n"
"    Atentament,<br><br>\n"
"    <u><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t></u><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street2\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street2\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.city or object.company_id.zip\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.zip or ''),(object.company_id.city or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.country_id\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.state_id and ('%s, ' % object.company_id.state_id.name) or ''),(object.company_id.country_id.name or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.phone\">\n"
"        Telèfon: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.website\">\n"
"        Web: <a t-if=\"object.company_id.website\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"></t></a><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <div>\n"
"        <img t-if=\"object.company_id.logo_url\" t-att-src=\"('/web/image/res.company/%s/logo' % object.company_id.id)\" style=\"width: 150px;\">\n"
"    </div>\n"
"    </p>\n"
"</div>\n"
"        "

#. module: cooperator
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cooperator.email_template_release_capital
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"    Hello <t t-out=\"object.subscription_request.firstname\"></t>,<br><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.payment_mode_id.payment_method_id.code == 'sepa_direct_debit'\">\n"
"    Your request to become member of Energy Community <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t> is already underway!<br><br>\n"
"    We will shortly issue a bank receipt to your bank account (<t t-out=\"object.subscription_request.iban\"></t>) for the collection of the initial mandatory contribution (<t t-out=\"object.amount_total\"></t> €).<br>\n"
"    Once we have been able to process this payment, you will receive a final welcome email where we will provide you with your membership number that will link you to the Energy Community <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>.<br><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-else=\"\">\n"
"    Your request to become member of Energy Community <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t> is already underway!<br>\n"
"    In order to complete it you must make a bank deposit of the amount indicated below:<br><br>\n"
"        - Initial registration fee amount: <t t-out=\"object.amount_total\"></t> €<br>\n"
"        - Banck account number: <t t-out=\"( object.company_id.bank_ids and object.company_id.bank_ids[0].acc_number ) or 'ESXX XXXX XXXX XX XXXXXXXXXX'\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Receiver: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Concept: Your first and last names<br><br>\n"
"    Once the payment is made, please send us the document proof of it by email to <t t-out=\"( object.company_id.coop_email_contact or object.company_id.email_formatted )\"></t><br><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    Seguim en contacte per qualsevol dubte.<br>\n"
"    <a href=\"https://somcomunitats.coop/recursos/\">Resources and FAQs</a><br><br>\n"
"    Atentament,<br><br>\n"
"    <u><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t></u><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street2\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street2\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.city or object.company_id.zip\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.zip or ''),(object.company_id.city or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.country_id\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.state_id and ('%s, ' % object.company_id.state_id.name) or ''),(object.company_id.country_id.name or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.phone\">\n"
"        Telèfon: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.website\">\n"
"        Web: <a t-if=\"object.company_id.website\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"></t></a><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <div>\n"
"        <img t-if=\"object.company_id.logo_url\" t-att-src=\"('/web/image/res.company/%s/logo' % object.company_id.id)\" style=\"width: 150px;\">\n"
"    </div>\n"
"    </p>\n"
"</div>\n"
msgstr ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"    <p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13px;\">\n"
"    Hola <t t-out=\"object.subscription_request.firstname\"></t>,<br><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.payment_mode_id.payment_method_id.code == 'sepa_direct_debit'\">\n"
"    La teva petició d'alta com a persona sòcia a la Comunitat Energètica <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t> està en tràmit!<br><br>\n"
"    En breu girarem un rebut bancari al teu compte (<t t-out=\"object.subscription_request.iban\"></t>) pel cobrament de l'aportació obligatòria inicial (<t t-out=\"object.amount_total\"></t> €).<br>\n"
"    Un cop hàgim pogut tramitar aquest cobrament rebràs un correu final de benvinguda on et donarem el teu número de sòcia que et vinculará amb la Comunitat Energètica <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>.<br><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-else=\"\">\n"
"    La teva petició d'alta com a persona sòcia a la Comunitat Energètica <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t> està en tràmit!<br>\n"
"    Per a completar el procés cal fer l'ingrés bancari de l'import indicat a continuació:<br><br>\n"
"        - Aportació inicial: <t t-out=\"object.amount_total\"></t> €<br>\n"
"        - Número de compte: <t t-out=\"( object.company_id.bank_ids and object.company_id.bank_ids[0].acc_number ) or 'ESXX XXXX XXXX XX XXXXXXXXXX'\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Beneficiari: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t><br>\n"
"        - Concepte: <i>--indica el teu nom i cognoms--</i><br><br>\n"
"    Una vegada fet l'ingrés, ens pots enviar el justificant de pagament responent aquest mateix correu electrònic o escrivint a <t t-out=\"( object.company_id.coop_email_contact or object.company_id.email_formatted )\"></t><br><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    Seguim en contacte per qualsevol dubte.<br>\n"
"    <a href=\"https://somcomunitats.coop/recursos/\">Resources and FAQs</a><br><br>\n"
"    Atentament,<br><br>\n"
"    <u><t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t></u><br>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.street2\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.street2\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.city or object.company_id.zip\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.zip or ''),(object.company_id.city or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.country_id\">\n"
"        <t t-out=\"('%s %s'%((object.company_id.state_id and ('%s, ' % object.company_id.state_id.name) or ''),(object.company_id.country_id.name or '')))\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.phone\">\n"
"        Telèfon: <t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"></t><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <t t-if=\"object.company_id.website\">\n"
"        Web: <a t-if=\"object.company_id.website\" t-att-href=\"object.company_id.website\"><t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"></t></a><br>\n"
"    </t>\n"
"    <div>\n"
"        <img t-if=\"object.company_id.logo_url\" t-att-src=\"('/web/image/res.company/%s/logo' % object.company_id.id)\" style=\"width: 150px;\">\n"
"    </div>\n"
"    </p>\n"
"</div>\n"

